title: Bug 47910ajc outjar jarfile does not contain MANIFEST.MF
OB: When using the outjar option in ajc, the resulting jar file does not contain the MANIFEST.MF file.
EB: If the outjar option is used, the resulting file should be a valid jar file with a METAINF/MANIFEST.MF file included.
SR: To reproduce the issue, execute ajc with the outjar option and verify that the resulting jar file does not contain the MANIFEST.MF file.
